Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.30,0:00:05.82,Raven,,0,0,0,,Jax. JAX. Put the controller\Ndown. Three world leaders said\N"months." MONTHS.
Dialogue: 1,0:00:00.30,0:00:05.82,Label,,0,0,0,,{\c&H0041D7FF&}RAVEN
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.92,0:00:10.35,Raven,,0,0,0,,The ones with the hats AND the\Nones without hats. All of them!
Dialogue: 1,0:00:05.92,0:00:10.35,Label,,0,0,0,,{\c&H0041D7FF&}RAVEN
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.45,0:00:18.15,Raven,,0,0,0,,I have a 47-page document. I\NLAMINATED it. The supply lines\Nare cut, Jax. The infrastructure\Nis collapsing.
Dialogue: 1,0:00:10.45,0:00:18.15,Label,,0,0,0,,{\c&H0041D7FF&}RAVEN
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.25,0:00:25.96,Raven,,0,0,0,,Are you even listening? I'm\Npricing bunkers on Craigslist.\NGary in Ohio has one. Reasonable\Nsquare footage.
Dialogue: 1,0:00:18.25,0:00:25.96,Label,,0,0,0,,{\c&H0041D7FF&}RAVEN
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.06,0:00:27.16,Raven,,0,0,0,,Nothing yet.
Dialogue: 1,0:00:26.06,0:00:27.16,Label,,0,0,0,,{\c&H0041D7FF&}RAVEN
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.26,0:00:28.36,Raven,,0,0,0,,What.
Dialogue: 1,0:00:27.26,0:00:28.36,Label,,0,0,0,,{\c&H0041D7FF&}RAVEN
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.46,0:00:31.94,Raven,,0,0,0,,You are playing a game while the\Nworld is ending.
Dialogue: 1,0:00:28.46,0:00:31.94,Label,,0,0,0,,{\c&H0041D7FF&}RAVEN
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.04,0:00:33.14,Raven,,0,0,0,,Jax —
Dialogue: 1,0:00:32.04,0:00:33.14,Label,,0,0,0,,{\c&H0041D7FF&}RAVEN
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.24,0:00:35.26,Raven,,0,0,0,,I hate you so much right now.
Dialogue: 1,0:00:33.24,0:00:35.26,Label,,0,0,0,,{\c&H0041D7FF&}RAVEN
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.76,0:00:34.86,Jax,,0,0,0,,Which ones?
Dialogue: 1,0:00:33.76,0:00:34.86,Label,,0,0,0,,{\c&H0064B9FF&}JAX
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.96,0:00:36.78,Jax,,0,0,0,,Okay but like — is that\Nconfirmed?
Dialogue: 1,0:00:34.96,0:00:36.78,Label,,0,0,0,,{\c&H0064B9FF&}JAX
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.88,0:00:37.98,Jax,,0,0,0,,Crazy.
Dialogue: 1,0:00:36.88,0:00:37.98,Label,,0,0,0,,{\c&H0064B9FF&}JAX
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.08,0:00:40.07,Jax,,0,0,0,,What'd you get me for the\Napocalypse?
Dialogue: 1,0:00:38.08,0:00:40.07,Label,,0,0,0,,{\c&H0064B9FF&}JAX
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.17,0:00:41.36,Jax,,0,0,0,,I got myself something.
Dialogue: 1,0:00:40.17,0:00:41.36,Label,,0,0,0,,{\c&H0064B9FF&}JAX
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.46,0:00:46.55,Jax,,0,0,0,,This game. Seventy hours of\Ncontent. Primitive survival\Nmechanics. Full resource\Nmanagement.
Dialogue: 1,0:00:41.46,0:00:46.55,Label,,0,0,0,,{\c&H0064B9FF&}JAX
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.65,0:00:57.38,Jax,,0,0,0,,Babe. Look at me. When the EMP\Nhits and we're living in a cave\N— do you want the guy who's\Nshaking? Or do you want the guy\Nwho already spent 70 hours\Nmastering Primitive Survival on\Na 4K OLED?
Dialogue: 1,0:00:46.65,0:00:57.38,Label,,0,0,0,,{\c&H0064B9FF&}JAX
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.48,0:00:59.86,Jax,,0,0,0,,I'm not playing a game, Raven.\NI'm training.
Dialogue: 1,0:00:57.48,0:00:59.86,Label,,0,0,0,,{\c&H0064B9FF&}JAX
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.96,0:01:01.95,Jax,,0,0,0,,You want a snack? I found some\Nbeans.
Dialogue: 1,0:00:59.96,0:01:01.95,Label,,0,0,0,,{\c&H0064B9FF&}JAX
